			</div>

			<!-- Text column -->
			<div class="flex items-center justify-center  px-12">
				<p class="pt-12 text-center text-sm md:text-3xl md:mx-4 text-left">
					We facilitate and deliver data-driven software and solutions for health service vendors and healthcare enterprises at petabyte scale, globally.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- bg-[#f2f7f9]  -->
		<div id="hdd" class="bg-opacity-100 z-20 relative py-8 shadow-md">
			<h1 class="text-xl md:text-5xl px-12 leading-tight md:leading-none md:px-32 font-bold pt-8 pb-4 md:pb-12 text-center text-[#194b92]">Designing Access to Health Data Discovery and Delivery</h1>
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:mx-32">
				<div id="hdd_col1" class="flex-1 p-4 md:w-1/4 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<p class="text-center font-thin md:text-left text-sm md:text-[1.75rem] italic md:leading-none px-12 md:px-0 md:pr-20"> "We are surrounded by locked-in silos of health data. Whether that lock-in is due to vendors, complexity, skills shortages or just the sheer amount of data being generated doesn't matter. Our goal at DesAcc is to build and deliver solutions for addressing data lock- in, enabling access to health data wherever and however it is stored."</p>
